name: Message Cupcakes
description:
You are ordering original Jeanine Cupcakery Cupcakes.

These cupcakes are made fresh to order in all of our sweet flavors!

This special order includes a message! How exciting!?

Sample Messages: 
"Happy Birthday!" 
"Great Job!"
"Congrats Grad!"
Etc.


All cupcakes must be ordered by the dozens. The number of cupcakes should correspond to the message letter count. 

Quantities: 
1 dozen (12 Cupcakes) 
2 dozen (24 Cupcakes)

4 dozen (48 Cupcakes)

name: Cupcake Bouquet
description:
One of our fan favorites, the cupcake bouquet is a perfect gift for birthdays, celebrations or just to say thanks! 

Small: Includes small vase and over 15 cupcakes
Medium: Includes medium sized vase and over 25 cupcakes
Large: Includes large sized vase and over 35 cupcakes

name: Monthly Surprise Flavor Box
description:
You are ordering original Jeanine Cupcakery Cupcakes. How exciting?!


This order is special, you can only order 9 cupcakes and the flavor is a total surprise! The flavors could range from a double-triple chocolate ganache or something like a Key West Cheesecake! That's the fun part! 

Every batch is special and prepared with love and care. We bake because we LOVE to bake. Every cupcake has our seal of approval, we're also perfectionists: everything has to be wonderful. 


We hope your experience with us is a sweet one! 

ORDERS:

If you have any questions, please email us!
